OL,3,CStuffed badger returns 'undamaged' to
OL,4,CLake District pub
OL,6,FA stuffed Badger has been returned to
OL,7,Fa Lake District pub after it was
OL,8,Fstolen on a staff night out.
OL,10,FThe 100-year-old badger, nicknamed
OL,11,F"Bertie" belongs to the Glen Rothay
OL,12,Fand Badger Bar in Rydal, near
OL,13,FAmbleside.
OL,15,FOn Monday 8 December, staff took
OL,16,FBertie to their Christmas meal at the
OL,17,FWhite Lion Hotel in Ambleside. Police
OL,18,Fsaid that while staff were out of the
OL,19,Froom, Bertie was taken from the
OL,20,Fbuilding by unknown males.
