OL,4,CLake District pub
OL,6,FIn a post on Facebook on 12 December,
OL,7,Fthe Glen Rothay confirmed that the
OL,8,Fbadger had been returned.
OL,10,FThey said: "Fantastic Friday night
OL,11,Fnews! Bertie has just staggered back
OL,12,Fthrough the front door!
OL,14,F"He seems to have had a merry time ,
OL,15,Fhis hat and tinsel have fallen off,
OL,16,Fand he's not telling what he's been up
OL,17,Fto. But he's been well looked after
OL,18,Fand we're grateful for that.
