OL,4,CLake District pub
OL,6,F"Thank you to everyone who cared
OL,7,Fenough to share Bertie's story and for
OL,8,Fthe fabulous publicity that has led to
OL,9,Fhis return."
OL,11,FStaff at the White Lion Hotel said:
OL,12,F"We are SO happy to see this tonight!
OL,13,FBertie has made it home safe and
OL,14,Fsound! He's had a very big adventure!"
OL,16,FThe Glen Rothay say that Bertie will
OL,17,Fnow be returned to his usual place on
OL,18,Fa rock beside the bar.
